"2436","of this 1st day of March 2001, as amended and restated as of November 7,"
"2437","2012, between Wells Fargo Funds Trust (the Trust), a business trust"
"2438","organized under the laws of the State of Delaware with its principal place"
"2439","of business at 525 Market Street, 12th Floor, San Francisco, California"
"2440","94163, Wells Fargo Funds Management, LLC (the Adviser), a limited"
"2441","liability company organized under the laws of the State of Delaware with"
"2442","its principal place of business at 525 Market Street, 12th Floor, San"
"2443","Francisco, California 94163, and Wells Capital Management Incorporated,"
"2444","a corporation organized under the laws of the State of California, with its"
