"4173","name Wells Fargo for any purpose; (iii) the Adviser or any corporate affiliate"
"4174","of the Adviser may use or grant to others the right to use the words Wells
Fargo, or any combination or abbreviation thereof, as all or a portion of a"
"4175","corporate or business name or for any commercial purpose, other than a grant of"
"4176","such right to another registered investment company not advised by the Adviser"
