"4178","thereof is no longer acting as investment adviser to the Fund, the Trust shall,"
"4179","upon request by the Adviser, promptly take such action as may be necessary to"
"4180","change its corporate name to one not containing the words Wells Fargo and"
"4181","following such change, shall not use the words Wells Fargo, or any combination"
"4182","thereof, as a part of its corporate name or for any other commercial purpose,"
"4183","and shall use its best efforts to cause its trustees, officers and shareholders"
"4184","to take any and all actions"
