"4481","composite performance record for inclusion in a Fund's documents, (A) the"
"4482","composite performance record of the Sub-Adviser's executive officers furnished"
"4483","to the Adviser and the Trust in writing prior to the date hereof (the Data) is"
"4484","true and correct, and has been prepared in accordance with applicable laws,"
"4485","rules, regulations, interpretations and in accordance with industry guidelines"
"4486","and standards with respect to standardized performance information; (B) there is"
"4487","no information material to an understanding of the Data which the Sub-Adviser"
