"4728","proceedings at law or in equity whether brought by a private party or a"
"4729","governmental department, commission, board, bureau, agency or instrumentality of"
"4730","any kind, arising out of or attributable to the willful misfeasance, bad faith,"
"4731","grossly negligent acts or reckless disregard of obligations or duties hereunder"
"4732","or the breach of any representation and warranty hereunder on the part of the"
"4733","Sub-Adviser or any of its officers, directors, employees affiliates or agents."
"4734","Notwithstanding the foregoing, the Sub-Adviser shall not be liable hereunder for"
"4735","any losses or damages resulting from the Sub-Adviser's adherence to the"
"4736","Adviser's written instructions, or for any action or inaction by the Sub-Adviser"
"4737","consistent with the Standard of Care described in Section 10 of this Agreement."
