"4796","     SECTION 20. WELLS FARGO NAME. The Sub-Adviser and the Trust each agree that"
"4797","the name Wells Fargo, which comprises a component of the Trust's name, is a"
"4798","property right of the parent of the Adviser. The Trust agrees and consents that:"
"4799","(i) it will use the words Wells Fargo as a component of its corporate name,"
"4800","the name of any series or class, or all of the above, and for no other purpose;"
"4801","(ii) it will not grant to any third party the right to use the name Wells
Fargo for any purpose; (iii) the Adviser or any corporate affiliate of the"
"4802","Adviser may use or grant to others the right to use the words Wells Fargo, or"
"4803","any combination or abbreviation thereof, as all or a portion of a corporate or"
"4804","business name or for any commercial purpose, other than a grant of such right to"
"4805","another registered investment company not advised by the Adviser or one of its"
"4806","affiliates; and (iv) in the event that the Adviser or an affiliate thereof is no"
"4807","longer acting as investment adviser to the Fund, the Trust shall, upon request"
"4808","by the Adviser, promptly take such action as may be necessary to change its"
"4809","corporate name to one not containing the words Wells Fargo and following such"
"4810","change, shall not use the words Wells Fargo, or any"
"4811","                                      -10-"
"4812","<PAGE>"
"4813","combination thereof, as a part of its corporate name or for any other commercial"
"4814","purpose, and shall use its best efforts to cause its trustees, officers and"
"4815","shareholders to take any and all actions that the Adviser may request to effect"
"4816","the foregoing and to reconvey to the Adviser any and all rights to such words."
"4817","The Sub-Adviser may include the Funds in its representative client list."
